**PUNISHMENT GUIDELINES**
Until v2 Moderation, this is with Dyno. Will change after.

__Previous Punishments__
!!modlogs <mention>

__Server / DM Advertising__
  Offense [1] Kick User for "Server / DM Advertising"
  Offense [2] Ban User for "Server / DM Advertising" with a duration of 3 days.
  Offense [3] Ban User for "Server / DM Advertising [Final]" permanently.

__Chat Spamming / Promoting Spam / Copy Pasta / Other Forms of Spam__
  Offense [1] Warn User for "Chat Spamming / Promoting Spam"
  Offense [2] Mute User for "Chat Spamming / Promoting Spam" with a duration of 6 hours.
  Offense [3] Mute User for "Chat Spamming / Promoting Spam" with a duration of 12 hours.
  Offense [4] Mute User for "Chat Spamming / Promoting Spam [Final]" permanently.

__Chat Disrepect / Racism [Ban for DM with Identical Length]__
  Offense [1] Warn User for "Targeted Disrespect / Racism"
  Offense [2] Mute User for "Targeted Disrespect / Racism" with a duration of 24 hours.
  Offense [3] Mute User for "Targeted Disrespect / Racism" with a duration of 12 days.
  Offense [4] Mute User for "Targeted Disrespect / Racism [Final]" permanently.

__Misc Bans__
  Server Raider [] Ban User for "Server Raiding / Abuse" permanently.
  Pornographic Content [] Ban User for "Inappropriate Images / Content" permanently.

__Misc Mutes__
  Interference [] Mute User for "Staff Interference" with a duration of 30 minutes.
  Impersonation [] Mute User for "Impersonation" with a duration of 2 hours.
